transcript:

Haa haa share catalog kar sakte ho yaha se aap quotation bhi de sakte ho quotation ka option pata hai aapko kaha se bhejte hai.
Nahi dekho ye jo three dot dikh raha hai aapko hello hello sir kaise ho sir sabse last me hai.
Executive: Sir aapne hamare customer ke number pe call kiya tha sir kya jankari sir India mart se baat kar raha hu services short create machines biometric machines me aap deal karte ho bataiye sir kya issue aa raha hai.
Customer: Ek to by lead jaldi aati nahi hai.
Aaati bhi hai to automatically sold ho jati hai mera ye problem hai.
Executive: Achcha sold out ho rahi hai.
Customer: Yes short create machines me aap deal karte ho sir aapne last 8 tarikh ko by lead consume ki thi short create machine ki theek hai Devendra ji se inse kya baat hui thi sir.
Executive: Wo log galat galat se inquiry karte hai bolte hai ki humko ye wala nahi dusra wala machine chahiye tha.
Customer: Achcha.
Hamko gate short gate machine chahiye tha bolte hai.
Executive: Achcha aur sir aapne ek aur 7 tarikh ko ek aur by lead consume ki thi pneumatic guniting machine inse bahar ka naam tha Ganesh Ganesh ji se baat hui thi aapki.
Customer: Ha baat hua tha.
Executive: Chota sa kam hai workout nahi hoga uska kam surat me tha.
Customer: Achcha wo surat ki lagi thi sahi keh rahe ho surat ka tha.
To abhi recently jo bhi jo bhi by lead mil rahi hai na mujhe wo kam ki nahi mil rahi hai khali time pass ki mil rahi hai theek hai aur jo kam ki jo kam ki jo by leads aa rahi hai wo automatically sold out ho ja rahi hai.
Executive: Last deal kab hui thi sir aapki India mart se.
Customer: Pune Pune se bhi aayi thi guniting services bol ke wo bhi sold out ho gayi Goa se aayi thi wo bhi sold out ho gayi.
Abhi Hyderabad Telangana se aayi thi teen bhi automatically stop ho gayi.
Executive: Kyu ho raha hai sir ye paisa bhi pura payment bhara hai aur mere ko service bhi barabar nahi mil rahi hai kya karne ka sir.
Customer: Ab yaha pe.
Executive: Dekho sir abhi mujhe ye puchna tha last deal aapki kab hui thi sir last deal.
Customer: Kya kya sir.
Executive: Last deal India mart se kab hua tha sir aapka.
Customer: Last deal matlab payment ka ha payment matlab buyer se deal kab hua tha aapka India mart se.
Last deal mere khyal se to July me hua tha July me.
Executive: July ka hua hai abhi tak July se abhi tak koi deal nahi hua hai sir aapka uske baad me koi bhi nahi hua hai.
Customer: Samajh gaya sir.
Executive: Theek hai aur sir abhi video meeting pe aap aa payenge main chahta hu video meeting ke bare me discuss kare isko kya dikkat aa rahi hai to dekhte hai kya hum kar sakte hai ho sakta hai kabhi kabhi sir keyword correction hota hai ya fir log search kar rahe hain jiski vajah se aapka catalog unko nahi dikh pa raha hai ek bar hum video meeting se dekh lete hai ki bhai dikkat kaha se aa rahi hai theek hai usko resolve kar denge sir fir abhi karna hai kya.
Customer: Sir time to dena padega na thoda sa jo issue aa raha hai sir usko jab tak samjhenge nahi tab tak kaise sahi karenge theek hai abhi kya karna padega mujhe.
Executive: Aapko video meeting pe aana padega sir aap phone se join kar payenge ya sir PC se join kar lenge aap video meeting.
Customer: Phone se phone se.
Executive: Phone se join kar lenge na theek hai to aap mujhe bas 5 minute ka time de do sir main aapke liye video meeting aapka arrange karke aap mail id bata do sir aapka mail id kya hai Kavita Kavita Rathore ji bilkul bilkul four bhi last me one hai na sir.
Customer: Ha yes yes.
Executive: Ha to main isse hi aapko abhi link bhej raha hu call kar raha hu sir hamari jo team aapke account manager hai wo aapko connect karengi aur sari cheez hum aapko guide karenge sir jo bhi problem aa rahi hogi sir please isko hum sahi karenge theek hai to aage se dikkat nahi aayegi theek hai na sir.
Customer: Theek hai theek hai sir okay.
Executive: Us par to kam karna fir bhi agar koi problem aati hai to bhi call kar sakte hai aap.
